title: Young Supporters Holiday Social
desc:
On November 30, we're celebrating the arrival of the Christmas season by celebrating generosity! 
 Spend the evening with? like-minded New Yorkers passionate about mercy and justice in the city, and support Hope for New York's work to strengthen more than 40 non-profits across New York City.? 
 At the event, you'll have the opportunity to start celebrating this season of giving by donating toward Hope for New York's work to strengthen more than 40 non-profits in New York City. 
 You'll also be able to meet other young New Yorkers passionate about seeing everyone in our city flourish.? 
 Food and drinks will be available for purchase. 
 Eat, drink, network, and celebrate generosity! Hope to see you! 
 Hosted by 2015-2016 Young Supporters Committee 
 Allyson Boudreaux Mylo Cheng Sarah Davis Soo Jeong Laura Kaufmann Melanie Luk Nithya Mathews Jacob Park Kayvan Rahbar Abigail Tseng Emily Webb Takuya Yamashita Andrea Yee
